Onboarding.Notified.CrossPaths: Get notified if you cross paths with someone who has anonymously reported themselves as positive for COVID-19 and get peace of mind when you don't.

Response.ReportingHelps:
Reporting your status is helping everyone stay safe and slowing the spread of COVID-19.

Your location will be used anonymously to help stop the spread of COVID-19.

Remember, we will never store or share any personal information.
